data.description: Don't miss your chance to own a piece of mountain paradise with endless possibilities. The open-concept layout flows seamlessly, providing ample space for both entertaining and everyday living. Two-bedroom home with an additional flex space for a work from home office, workout room, or just a space to be creative. Relax on the front porch with a cup of Joe in the morning and finish the day on the back deck, enjoying the long-range mountain views while taking in the sunset. In addition to its charm and comfort, 2 Clarks Chapel Extension also offers exciting potential as a "short-term" rental property. With its desirable location near quaint downtown Weaverville and Vibrant Asheville plus all the outdoor activities that WNC has to offer.  This almost new and well-kept home with its and proximity to Weaverville, Asheville, Mars Hill, Marshall & Hot Springs is an excellent opportunity for investors looking to capitalize on the thriving vacation rental market, or for your family to enjoy!
